title: Home Gym Workout Station, Multifunctional Home Gym System with Leg Extension, Leg Press, Preacher Curl and Full Body Exercise Accessories, Plate Loaded Strength Training Machine
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Home Gym Systems
features: Full Body Workout Station: Our home gym station is an all in one strength training machine for full body workouts. You can perform various kinds of exercises with this workout station such as chest press, chest fly, lat pull down, ab crunch, leg extension, leg press, seated row, preacher curl, kick back, side leg raise and so on. You are able to get full body training at home, which develops your muscles on your arms, back, legs, chest, shoulders and glutes.

All the Components Include: This home gym system comes with full body training attachments, which includes 1x lat pull down bar, 1x row bar, 1x ab shoulder strap, 2x handle grips, 1x ankle strap, 1x leg press pedal, 1x preacher pad, 1x storage post, 2x 1inch barbell clamps and 2x 2inch barbell clamps. You are able to get the workout station and all the attachments needed in only one purchase, which will save your time and money.

Plate Loaded Home Gym: This home gym station adopts plate loaded design, which means you can load more weights than the ones using weight stacks. You can easily load up to 400lbs weights on this machine. The diameter of the loading bars is 1inch and the 2inch removable adapters are also included. You are free to load both 1inch standard weight plates and 2inch olympic weight plates on this home gym.

Heavy Duty Construction: Constructed with 2"x 2", 14 gague steel, superior powder coating, premium quality paddings and high tensile strength sturdy aircraft cables. assembled size: 69.7"x 42.2"x 80.6". gross weight: 162 lbs. This home gym station will last for long term use. The seat pad, preacher pad, leg press pedal and leg rollers are all adjustable, which allows users with different body shapes to use this machine.
This home gym station will be arrived in 2 packages, which may be not arrived at the same time.

title: Sunny Health & Fitness Premium Squat Smith Machine Power Rack – High Load Capacity, Adjustable Height, Pull-Up Bar, Spotter Blocks – For Versatile Strength Training, Weightlifting, Squats, Bench Press
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Racks & Cages › Smith Machines
features: OLYMPIC-STYLE: Perfect your form and weightlift like the pros with the Smith Machine Squat Rack Essential Series II. Designed with smooth, cylindrical guide rails, the machine safely assists your movements, so you get the most out of each lift.
SMOOTH RAILS: These cylindrical guide rails are built to aid your lifts and promote proper form. Enjoy smooth and quiet movement during your workouts.
SPOTTER BLOCKS: These durable spotter arms are built for safety. Not only are adjustable to accommodate your height but also to add in varying movements like back squats and deadlifts.
THREE-IN-ONE: Use the machine for weightlifting, resistance band workouts, and a 3-level height adjustable pull-up bar. Put your physical fitness to the test! No pain, no gain.
ADJUSTABILITY: Highly adjustable with 13 different height settings, this rack can adjust to your body type. Just simply slide and set the J-Hooks or any attachment to your preference.

RESISTANCE BAND ANCHORS: Increase power and strength by implementing resistance bands during your weightlifting. Easily attach bands onto the anchors towards the bottom of the guide rails on both sides of the machine.
2” BAR: Designed with a 2-inch, heavy duty steel bar and plate storage, this machine is built to be compatible with standard sized weight plates and accessories.

ANGLED PULL-UP BAR: This pull-up bar is adjustable up to 3 heights and is designed with a multi-grip bar. Maximize your upper body strength by targeting specific upper body muscle groups depending on your grip.

FITNESS APP EXPERIENCE: Download and join the SunnyFit community to access an array of free, professional trainer-led strength workouts and hundreds of other fitness programs. In the app, track your progress, set fitness goals, access personalized workout plans, and compete with other community members to get to the top of the leaderboard. Have any workout of your choice right at your fingertips, while also feeling supported and inspired as a member of this likeminded community.
The SF-XF920021 Squat Smith Machine Power Rack is compatible with the following add ons: SF-BH620037, SF-BH620038, SF-BH6920, SF-BH6921, SF-BH622045, SF-BH6996, SF-XFA006

3 start and end positions can meet the needs of people with different heights. Adjustable height range: 47.8'' to 62''. All your family members can enjoy the fun of leg strength training.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
How to Use 
Please put the TENS unit massager on your skin before start.Try to increase intensity of out put one by one and wait for about 10 seconds if no pulse is sensed. (People has different sensation levels) 
1.Press the ON button, the first blue light on;
2. Press the ON button again, The first light flash, and you will get the pulse massage.
3.Press INC to increase the tens level;Press DEC to decrease the tens level;
4.Press the PROGRAM To choose the mode,Press the OFF turn off the machine.
ATTENTION 
The skin with too much hair will affect the pulse effect. Please turn off the device before you touch the pads. 
Not for pregnants.
Not for heart patientsor those carry metal inthe body.
Not for people with deepvein thrombosis (DVT).
Not for people with severe hypertension

Product Description
ERGONOMIC HANDLES 
Curved, contoured handles add potential variations to your grip and workouts Ergonomic design aids in comfort when performing assisted squats. 
EXTRA RESISTANCE 
Featuring 4 resistance bands rated at 22 LB each, the Row-N-Ride Plus increases the intensity of your assisted squats and helps to shape your glutes, thighs, and legs. 
PADDED SEAT 
The thick and supple cushioned seat provides just the right amount of support. It supports 4 levels of lateral adjustability and 3 levels of default incline positions. 
DIGITAL MONITOR 
Stay focused on your goals and track your progress with the Digital Monitor which tracks: Calories, Count, Reps/Min, Time and includes a Scan function. 
HIGH MAX WEIGHT 
This foldable squat assist exercise equipment is designed for powerful workouts. A 300 LB max weight gives you the confidence to push for the extra rep and go the distance. 
NON-SLIP FOOT PEDALS 
Its self-leveling pedals help you to get in and out of the bike in a breeze. Stable end caps prevent any movement to ensure you have a stable and safe workout. 
CONVENIENCE 
Easily store almost anywhere in your home. Remove the knob, fold, and store; as easy as 1, 2, 3. 
EXERCISE IDEAS 
MAXIMUM RANGE 
Saddle angle control allows you to adjust the saddle at 30, 60, and 90 degrees giving you deeper squat positions 
BENT OVER ROW 
Single arm upright rows help to strengthen your back and biceps, and can easily be completed by dismounting your Row-N-Ride and pulling up and back on the seat. 
DEADLIFT 
The Row-N-Ride can even be used to complete deadlifts, which are great for targeting the posterior chain muscles like the glutes, hamstrings, calves, and core! 
INCLINE CHEST PRESS 
Challenge your upper chest, shoulders, and core muscles as you press up on the seat of your Row-N-Ride to complete incline chest press.

Can the ShredForce be used for leg workouts too? 
No - the ShredForce is specifically made to help you train your upper body, so it won't be safe to use as a leg trainer. 
When storing my ShredForce, should it be open or closed? 
The best way to store it is to lower the resistance level and close the arm exerciser. This way your hydraulics will stay in outstanding condition for much longer. 
Do the hydraulics on the exerciser leak oil during training? 
Absolutely not. The premium hydraulics built into the ShredForce are durable and made to feel absolutely outstanding during workouts - no leaks, no other issues. 
Who can benefit from the ShredForce? 
The compact form combined with a wide resistance range makes the ShredForce a great option for traveling athletes, people just getting back into training, folks who live in smaller spaces, and anyone who needs an extra boost of upper body strength. 
Will the ShredForce replace my dumbbells? 
While most people will be perfectly satisfied with the upper body workouts they can perform with the Shredforce, it isn't made to be a direct replacement for dumbbells, but rather a complement that covers the needs your dumbbells don't.

The patented portable Dip Station with adjustable width to correctly fit you and every member of your family 
The only width adjustable Dip Station 
Angled grips and adjustable width engage the right muscles with proper form. A Dip Station that fits reduces strain on the shoulders, elbows and wrists so you can get the right results in less time.

The Original Dip Bar Fitness Station 
Get effective workouts at home and on the go 
Get Ultimate results, versatility and value with the Dip Bar Fitness Station. Rapidly build chest, shoulders, arms and core with better workouts every day. 
Thick 1.5 inch steel tubing and 3 foot tall frame is suitable for users up to 6'5” and 350 lbs 
Angled grips and adjustable width sets the grips from 19 to 24 inches to provide a proper fit for you and every member of your family

Rapid Results, Core Strength, Balanced Development, and Assisted Exercise Variation 
The Fit that Promotes Form 
Dips rapidly build a sculpted upper body when supported with good form. Proper position of the shoulders, wrists, and arms reduces strain and engages the right muscles so you can focus on repetition. Width position I at 19” fits most users up to 190lbs and position II at 24" fits users up to 350lbs. 
Build Core Strength 
L-Sits and Knee Raises tone core and strengthen lower back. Adjustable leveling feet and high density foam grips provide stability and comfort for longer workouts. Simple color coded assembly, no tools required! 
Balance Chest and Back with Bodyweight Rows 
Compound Bodyweight exercises deliver the fastest results including full bodyweight rows to balance chest and shoulder development. Innovative design supports up to 350 lbs for users up to 6 feet 5 inches and folds for easy storage. 
Assisted Exercise Variation 
Assisted exercise variations let you easily control resistance for complete full intensity workouts right from day one. Supercharge your metabolism with strength training and interval workouts that get fast effective results. 
Easy Portability and Set-Up 
The Ultimate Body Press Dip Bar Fitness Station is sized for you and your home workout space so you can leave it set up and ready to go. But it's also easy to fold it down after each use for storage under a bed, in the closet, or in the trunk of your car. 
Fast Color Coded Assembly with Quick Release Pins 
The Dip Station ships in four pieces to allow the handles to rotate into a flat position and to enable our patented adjustable width positions. Assembly and disassembly takes just moments with integrated quick release clips and color coded sections. 
Integrated leveling feet adjust for perfect stability 
Integrated leveling feet ensure your Dip Station is always sitting perfectly flat on the floor for optimum stability. Each corner is adjustable with 8 positions to give you total placement flexibility. 
Pro Tip: Ensure maximum stability by positioning the feet at the outer four corners of the base bars. 
Align your Dip Station to Finish your Set-Up 
The Dip Station is engineered for easy disassembly and folding. You will notice a small degree of play in the 4 sections that firms up once your bodyweight is applied. This is to prevent the sections from locking together during use, preventing disassembly. After set-up, ensure that your dip station handles are at the correct angles by aligning the seams at the front and back floor sections as shown in the illustration.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Check it out! The Panther is the ultimate destination for your home gym journey 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Does this machine come with all the bells and whistles, or do I have to buy extra stuff? 
Oh, it’s got all the bells and whistles, my friend. No need to go hunting for extra gear. You’ve got your Smith machine, pec deck, cable pulley system, pull-up bars... it’s a one-stop shop for your entire workout. Just bring your muscles. 
What’s with the 7-degree angled Smith machine? Does that actually make a difference? 
Oh yeah, big time! That 7-degree angle isn’t just for looks—it’s all about smoother, more natural movement. No more “joint grinds” that feel like you’re wrestling with the machine. You’ll feel like you're lifting with the pros. 
Can I actually fit this beast in my garage, or is it gonna need its own room? 
It’s a powerhouse, but we designed it to save space. Think of it like a Transformer—big performance, compact design. It'll fit in your garage or home gym without turning it into a circus tent. 
What’s the deal with the cable ratios? 
No calculators needed! Here's the breakdown: 
4:1 on the pulley system 
2:1 on the pec deck 
1:1 on the low row 
Mix these ratios, and you’ve got versatile training for every muscle, every angle. It’s like having a whole gym in one machine! 
Is the pec deck on this machine really as good as it sounds, or is it just a gimmick? 
Nope, no gimmicks here! The built-in pec deck is smooth, comfy, and hits your chest just right. Adjustable settings let you customize for the perfect stretch and contraction. It's like having a trainer, minus the sweat!

description: Product DescriptionSay goodbye to stagnant workouts and unlock your full potential with the Perfect Pushup Elite. Designed to revolutionize your exercise routine, these innovative push-up handles help you maximize muscle engagement. The push-up handles utilize precision-engineered steel ball bearings to enable smooth and effortless rotation, minimizing friction for a comfortable, natural movement, while simultaneously activating additional stabilizer muscles in your arms, shoulders, chest, back, and abs, resulting in increased strength and greater definition. Ergonomic TPE grips ensure weight distribution is even and comfortable, reducing pressure points and wrist and elbow strain, while the soft, textured surface prevents slippage for a secure hold during every rep. In addition, elevated handles provide a neutral grip to help you maintain proper form so you can focus on perfecting your push-up technique. Perform your push-ups without worrying about slipping or sliding, thanks to bottom-surface treads that provide a secure grip on any floor type. With a weight capacity of 400 pounds, the Perfect Pushup Elite accommodates athletes of all sizes and body types, including those utilizing weight vests for added resistance. Plus, its generous 8-inch diameter base ensures exceptional stability, allowing you to focus solely on your workout without any distractions.Amazon.comTake your pushups to the next level with the Champion Perfect V2 pushup handles. The handles are designed to rotate slightly during your pushups, increasing muscle activation as you dip lower. As a result, you can increase your muscle strength and definition in your arms, shoulders, back, chest, and abs. The handles also reduce joint strain in your wrists and elbows through natural body movement, with ergonomic grips that help distribute weight evenly and reduce pressure points. And thanks to the handles' off-road-style tread, the Perfect V2 handles securely grip all floor surfaces. Designed to support users up to 400 pounds, the handles come with a U.S. Navy SEAL-inspired 21-day workout chart.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
PIVOTING SEAT AND KNEEPAD 
Go further in your stretches with a travel distance of over 24 inches. Large, cushioned seating and knee pad provide exceptional comfort and support. 
DUAL SAFETY STRAPS 
2 pairs of safety straps located on the front post of the stretch machine will help ensure the safe operation of the stretch trainer machine. 
INSTRUCTIONAL PLACARD 
Detailed instructions for 9 different stretches help you get started on your stretching regimen. 
SELF-LEVELING PEDALS 
Never lose your step and recover quickly for your next stretch position. 
MULTI-GRIP HANDLES 
Switch grips to assist in targeting and focusing on specific areas or positions. 
FOAM ROLLERS 
Kick your feet up, decompress, and stretch using the padded foam rollers. 
HAMSTRING 
Hold the ropes or lower handlebar with the palms facing down. Extend one leg up, placing your foot on the foam pad straightening your leg. To intensify the stretch in your hamstring, keep your chest open, and reach for the upper handlebar, switch sides. 
QUADRICEPS 
Stand at the front of your machine, facing away from your machine. Bring one foot up, resting your toes on the foam pad. Press into the stretch on the front side of your leg. Use the upper handlebar for balance. Keep your body neutral, switch sides. 
LOWER BACK 
Start with the seat in its forward position, holding the upper handlebar or ropes with palms facing down. Sink your weight into the seat, allowing gravity to pull you slowly deeper into a lower back stretch. 
UPPER BACK 
Hold ropes or upper handlebar with palms facing upward. Allow gravity to slowly tilt the seat back. To target the different areas of your upper back and neck slowly roll your head to the right, left, and down, or up, pausing where it feels good. 
INNER THIGHS, GROIN 
Hold the ropes or the lower handlebar with palms facing down. With seat forward, place soles of your feet together, resting on the lower pad and pressing knees out. Slowly tilt the seat back, lengthening the upper body to deepen the stretch. 
HAMSTRING, IT BAND, HIPS, BACK 
Hold the right side of the ropes or lower handlebar with palms facing down. Extend the leg up to the right side. Lean into your left side to deepen the stretch. Complete the stretch and repeat on the right leg.

Upgrade your home gym with the Valor Fitness Stationary Upright Weight Bench, built for strength training and intense workouts. Heavy-Duty Stationary Upright Weight Bench for Home Gyms and Strength Training 
Elevate your fitness routine with our Heavy-Duty Stationary Upright Weight Bench, the ultimate addition to your home gym or light-commercial setup. Designed to support your most intense seated workouts, this bench combines durability, functionality, and comfort, making it a must-have for anyone serious about strength training and upper body exercises. 
Key Features and Benefits: 
Heavy-Duty Steel Construction: Built with a robust 2.75” x 2” solid steel frame and a stable tripod base, this bench ensures unwavering stability even during your heaviest lifts. Rubber-capped feet provide a non-slip foundation and protect your floors from scratches, making it perfect for home gym setups.
Ergonomic Design for Comfort and Posture: Featuring a back pad with a slight tilt and a tapered seat positioned 18.5” off the ground, this bench supports a natural upright posture for enhanced comfort and performance. The thoughtful design reduces strain on your lower back while maximizing upper body engagement.
Versatile Training Options: This multi-functional weight bench supports a wide range of exercises, including seated shoulder presses, bicep curls, triceps extensions, lateral raises, and core stabilization exercises. Its 750 lbs weight capacity makes it suitable for users at all fitness levels, from beginners to advanced athletes.
Enhanced Stability with Foot Support: Equipped with knurled foot pegs for added grip, the bench provides extra support for maintaining proper form during heavy lifts. The sturdy foot posts let you focus on your workout without compromising on balance or safety.
High-Density Dual-Layered Padding: The durable and resilient padding is crafted to withstand daily wear and tear while offering optimal comfort and support during extended workout sessions. The padding resists flattening over time, ensuring long-lasting performance.
Compact and Space-Saving Design: With dimensions of 42” x 25.5” x 42”, this stationary upright bench offers a small footprint, making it ideal for home gyms, garages, and compact workout spaces. Its sleek design fits seamlessly into your fitness area without taking up unnecessary space.
Commercial-Grade Quality: Built to light-commercial standards, this bench is perfect not just for home gym enthusiasts but also for small fitness studios. Its durable construction and thoughtful design cater to both individual and shared use.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
The world's first folding home gym Smith Machine with a pulley system, designed for small spaces without sacrificing quality or functionality 
Altas Strength Folding Home Gym Smith Machine 3101 with Pulley System – Compact, Full-Body Workout for Strength Training at Home 
Revolutionize Your Home Gym with the Altas Strength 3101 Folding Home Gym Smith Machine Whether you’re limited on space or simply want to make the most out of your workout area, this Smith Machine is your all-in-one answer. With its innovative Four Steps Folding design, it can reduce its depth from 49 inches to an ultra-compact 22 inches—giving you the freedom to store it easily when not in use. 
Key Features of the Altas Strength 3101 
Space-Saving Four Steps Folding: Transform your gym from a depth of 49” to just 22” with this easy-to-fold design. Adjust the Smith bar and pulley together in the middle, lock the sides, and fold down the chin-up station—saving space without sacrificing function.
All-In-One Functional Trainer: Featuring a power rack, Smith machine, functional trainer, leg press, chin-up station, dip station, suspension trainer, and low row, this machine covers all your strength training needs.
Heavy-Duty Construction: Built with a heavy-duty frame and commercial-grade guide rails for smooth, controlled movements, allowing you to focus on perfecting your form while reducing the risk of injury.
Powerful Pulley System: Includes steel aircraft cables rated to 2,000 lbs and two 220 lb weight stacks, offering limitless training options for exercises like lat pulldowns, rows, and more.
Safety and Convenience: Designed for private, safe workouts at home, the Smith machine features a safe lock and release system along with safety catches, ensuring you can push yourself to the limit without the need for a spotter.
Why Choose the Altas Strength 3101 Folding Home Gym Smith Machine? 
Ideal for Compact Spaces: When space is a premium, the ALTAS STRENGTH 3101 shines. Its unique folding design allows it to occupy half the footprint of a traditional Smith machine, making it the perfect choice for small home gyms, apartments, or limited workout areas.
Full-Body Workouts at Home: Squat, press, lunge, deadlift, and more—all within the safety and stability of the guided Smith machine bar. The integrated pulley system adds even more versatility for pulling exercises, cable crossovers, and functional training.
Commercial-Grade at Home: Designed for home use but built like a club machine, the ALTAS STRENGTH 3101 offers the same high-quality performance you would expect at the gym.
No More Gym Commutes: Get all the benefits of a professional gym without the hassle of membership fees or commuting. You can enjoy private, effective training at any time.
The Smith Machine Advantage Smith machines are known for their ability to stabilize the barbell during exercises, making them ideal for controlled movements like squats, presses, deadlifts, and lunges. The ALTAS STRENGTH 3101 takes this advantage even further by incorporating a pulley system for functional exercises and an all-in-one design that combines the best of home and commercial gym equipment. 
Transform from a depth of 49” to 22” in four Steps Folding 
The First Step 
Adjust the smith bar and pulley together in the middle of the smith Rack.
Open the pin locks and screw nuts on the left and right sides.
The Second Step 
Place the smith bar vertically to the left side.
The Third Step 
open pin lock and put down chin up station.
The Fourth Step 
Close the left and right frames to complete the fold. Transform from a depth of 49” to 22”.
This is a world first for Folding Home Gym Smith Machine. All-In-One Functional Trainer upgrade to the fitness Solution.

Engineered with space in mind, ALTAS STRENGTH 3101 can transform from a depth of 54” to as little as 22” in less than 30 seconds.

One of the standout features of this Olympic free-weight rack is its built-in weight stack, ingeniously integrated into the machine's frame. This innovative design allows for easy organization and accessibility of weights, enabling users to engage in intense weightlifting or strength training from the comfort of their own home. 
Furthermore, the Folding Home Gym Smith Machine boasts a versatile pulley system with dual heavy-duty swivel pulleys on the power rack. With 17 different height adjustments, this pulley system enables users to perform a wide range of exercises, making it a truly versatile and indispensable fitness equipment. 
Embrace the convenience, space-saving design, and unlimited workout possibilities that this cutting-edge equipment brings to your doorstep. Say goodbye to gym commutes and hello to your own private, fully-equipped fitness haven. 
The stacks 
2 x 220lbs precision cut steel weight stacks allow the user to increase strength over time with 22 weight increments. These easy to access, pin select weight stacks add ease for quick-changing supersets, multiple users and much more.

Functional Trainer

Includes 6 functional trainer attachments and 2 x 220lbs integrated weight stacks located at the back of the unit for the ultimate strength training workout. modules.title: The world's first folding home gym Smith Machine with a pulley system, designed for small spaces without sacrificing quality or functionality  Altas Strength Folding Home Gym Smith Machine 3101 with Pulley System – Compact, Full-Body Workout for Strength Training at Home
modules.text:
Revolutionize Your Home Gym with the Altas Strength 3101 Folding Home Gym Smith Machine Whether you’re limited on space or simply want to make the most out of your workout area, this Smith Machine is your all-in-one answer. With its innovative Four Steps Folding design, it can reduce its depth from 49 inches to an ultra-compact 22 inches—giving you the freedom to store it easily when not in use. 
Key Features of the Altas Strength 3101 
Space-Saving Four Steps Folding: Transform your gym from a depth of 49” to just 22” with this easy-to-fold design. Adjust the Smith bar and pulley together in the middle, lock the sides, and fold down the chin-up station—saving space without sacrificing function.
All-In-One Functional Trainer: Featuring a power rack, Smith machine, functional trainer, leg press, chin-up station, dip station, suspension trainer, and low row, this machine covers all your strength training needs.
Heavy-Duty Construction: Built with a heavy-duty frame and commercial-grade guide rails for smooth, controlled movements, allowing you to focus on perfecting your form while reducing the risk of injury.
Powerful Pulley System: Includes steel aircraft cables rated to 2,000 lbs and two 220 lb weight stacks, offering limitless training options for exercises like lat pulldowns, rows, and more.
Safety and Convenience: Designed for private, safe workouts at home, the Smith machine features a safe lock and release system along with safety catches, ensuring you can push yourself to the limit without the need for a spotter.
Why Choose the Altas Strength 3101 Folding Home Gym Smith Machine? 
Ideal for Compact Spaces: When space is a premium, the ALTAS STRENGTH 3101 shines. Its unique folding design allows it to occupy half the footprint of a traditional Smith machine, making it the perfect choice for small home gyms, apartments, or limited workout areas.
Full-Body Workouts at Home: Squat, press, lunge, deadlift, and more—all within the safety and stability of the guided Smith machine bar. The integrated pulley system adds even more versatility for pulling exercises, cable crossovers, and functional training.
Commercial-Grade at Home: Designed for home use but built like a club machine, the ALTAS STRENGTH 3101 offers the same high-quality performance you would expect at the gym.
No More Gym Commutes: Get all the benefits of a professional gym without the hassle of membership fees or commuting. You can enjoy private, effective training at any time.
The Smith Machine Advantage Smith machines are known for their ability to stabilize the barbell during exercises, making them ideal for controlled movements like squats, presses, deadlifts, and lunges. The ALTAS STRENGTH 3101 takes this advantage even further by incorporating a pulley system for functional exercises and an all-in-one design that combines the best of home and commercial gym equipment.

modules.title: Folding Home Gym Smith Machine  Innovative All-In-One Fitness Solution with Space-Saving Design
modules.text:
Altas Strength, a leading fitness equipment manufacturer based in Canada, has revolutionized home gym setups with their groundbreaking Folding Home Gym Smith Machine. Designed with space constraints in mind, this state-of-the-art machine can transform from a depth of 54" to as little as 22" in less than 30 seconds, all without compromising exercise functionality. 
One of the standout features of this Olympic free-weight rack is its built-in weight stack, ingeniously integrated into the machine's frame. This innovative design allows for easy organization and accessibility of weights, enabling users to engage in intense weightlifting or strength training from the comfort of their own home. 
Furthermore, the Folding Home Gym Smith Machine boasts a versatile pulley system with dual heavy-duty swivel pulleys on the power rack. With 17 different height adjustments, this pulley system enables users to perform a wide range of exercises, making it a truly versatile and indispensable fitness equipment. 
Embrace the convenience, space-saving design, and unlimited workout possibilities that this cutting-edge equipment brings to your doorstep. Say goodbye to gym commutes and hello to your own private, fully-equipped fitness haven.

Product Description
Valor Fitness Upright Weight Bench - Heavy-Duty Stationary Bench for Advanced Strength Training 
Durable Construction for Stability and Floor Protection 
The Valor Fitness Upright Weight Bench is built with a solid steel frame, measuring 2.75” x 2”, providing unmatched durability and support during intense strength training sessions. The tripod frame design, reinforced with a rear U-shaped base, ensures maximum stability, even under heavy loads. This heavy-duty construction is perfect for seated exercises like shoulder presses, bicep curls, and lateral raises. 
For added safety and gym floor protection, each foot is encased with rubber end caps, which enhance grip and prevent slipping. These caps also safeguard your flooring from potential damage, making this bench ideal for home or light-commercial gyms. Designed to handle the demands of heavy lifting, the Valor Fitness Upright Weight Bench combines a sturdy frame with thoughtful features to enhance your workout performance and protect your workout environment. 
Ergonomic Padding for Comfort and Support During Workouts 
The Valor Fitness Upright Weight Bench features a high-density, dual-layered padded seat and backrest, designed to provide superior comfort and durability during intense strength training. Engineered to withstand the stress and pressure of heavy workouts, this padding ensures optimal support for your back and hips, allowing you to focus on your exercises without discomfort. 
The back pad measures 19.75” x 9.75” x 2”, while the seat pad measures 12” x 9.5” x 2”, offering ample cushioning for a secure and comfortable sitting position. title: Seated Dip Machine Plate Loaded- Tricep Dip Press Machine with Cable Bar for Biceps Chest Training, Hold up to 400LBS
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Upper Body Machines
features: [Versatile Upper Body Training Machine]- The seated triceps dip machine allows for focused and isolated workouts. Its convergent motion ensures that the triceps muscles are activated for maximum exercise effectiveness. In addition, the triceps press machine comes with a cable bar for doing biceps exercises like upright cable rows and biceps curls. It's a versatile machine that engages the muscles of the arms, shoulder and chest to take your upper body strength training to the next level!

[Improved Arms and Machine Design]- The seated dip machine is a safer and more effective alternative to traditional tricep dips, which can cause strain on the wrists and shoulders. With stable and controllable movements, this seated dip station minimizes the risk of injuries. Additionally, the tricep pushdown machine features a rotating handle that can be adjusted to fit varying shoulder widths, providing multiple grip options to target different areas of the triceps muscles.

[Personalized Adjustments]- It offers easy-to-use personalization adjustments, allowing you to customize your workout to suit your varying fitness levels and training goals with simple weight plate adjustments. Even beginners can experience challenging workouts without requiring extensive technical skills or coordination. The seat height and cable bar length can be adjusted to accommodate different body types, ensuring maximum comfort and efficiency during your exercise routine.

[High Quality Material]- The plate loaded tricep machine is composed of heavy-duty steel and premium coatings, making it durable and stable. The comfortable, sweat-resistant seat and backrest provide ample support for intense workouts and long-term use. Measuring only 42.7"x26.2"x51.2", it's the ideal size for any space in your home gym. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 LBS and compatibility with 1" and 2" weight plates, it can meet your most daily training needs. (Plates are not included)

[Easy to Use Step]- The tricep press machine is also featured by simplicity in use. To give your triceps a serious workout, all you need to do is choose the right weights, adjust the seat height, and grab onto the narrow handles. If you want to give your lower chest muscles some extra attention, just lean forward ever so slightly and switch to the wide handle. To perform a bicep curl, rise to your feet and plant them firmly on a rugged steel plate, then you can exercise freely with cable handle.

title: Valor Fitness Chest Press Machine – Independent Converging Arms - 9 Adjustable Positions - Flat Incline - 250 Pound Max - Home Gym Equipment BF-47
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Benches › Adjustable Benches
description: The Valor Fitness Adjustable Flat or Incline Chest Bench Press offers an innovative solution for training workouts, providing a safe and efficient way to build strength. Designed with independent converging arms that come together, it allows for varied weight levels on each arm, catering to individual strength needs or focused single arm training. Perfect for home gym and light-commercial gym settings, this bench press's adjustable features and independent arms offer a tailored workout experience. The additional storage pegs help maintain a clean workout space, making it a valuable addition to any fitness enthusiast's equipment collection.
features: HEAVY DUTY- Constructed with 2” x 2” steel frame with high-density, dual-layered pad measuring 44” x 9. 5” x 2”. U-shaped base ensures strength and durability throughout frame while ankle pads provide safety to user during ab crunch function.

CONVERGING ARMS- Each arm operates independently of each other, allowing user to place variable weight levels on each arm if needed or simply to strengthen one side at a time. Arms converge to the middle to effectively target chest muscles. 1” plate pegs.
ADJUSTABLE- Safety catch with protective rubber strip has 9 adjustment positions for an 8” range. Adjusted with locking pin for safety. Ankle pads can be adjusted between 2 different positions.

VERSATILE- Can be used as a flat bench press, incline bench press, or ab crunch board. Folding base to perform incline bench press and ab crunches. Ankle padding beneath the head of the bench supports knees and ankles and allows ab crunch function.

ADDITIONAL- Max weight load 125 lb per arm, 250 lb total. Also includes 2 plate storage pegs, each measuring 8” long and 1” in diameter, allows a clean and organized home gym. Meant for home and light-commercial use.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Chest Press Machine with Independent Converging Arms for a Unique Workout 
Adjustable Flat or Incline Chest Bench Press with Ab Crunch Feature 
The extra long seat pad allows the user to adjust their position for a different range of motion or to target the muscles from a different angle. The high-density, dual-layered pad folds down for the incline bench feature and acts as an ab crunch board. The foam ankle pads secure the user and support ankles and knees when performing ab crunches. The safety catches allow each arm to be rested when not in use and protect the user in the event the lift cannot be completed. Each safety catch, featuring a protective rubber strip, has 9 different adjustment positions using a locking pin, allowing an 8” range. A plate storage peg is featured on both sides of the unit to allow a clean and organized home gym. 
Each weight & storage peg measures 8” long and 1” in diameter. To convert plate storage pegs to 2" for Olympic style plates, the EX-10 adaptor is sold separately. 
This weight bench station has a Maximum Weight load of 125 lbs per arm, allowing users to train with up to 250 lbs. total. 
Maximize Your Home Gym Workout - Upper Body & Core Routines 
Flat Bench- Chest Press 
Flat bench presses are best for overall development of the pectoralis, commonly known as the pecs or your chest muscles. With this natural and fluid movement, it is likely to assist you in daily life activities as well as other exercises! 
Incline Bench - Chest Press 
With a similar movement to the flat bench, performing incline bench presses will activate your shoulders as well as the upper part of the pecs. The incline press puts less strain on your rotator cuff while activating the deltoids. 
Ab Crunch Feature 
Using the high density pad supports by the head of the bench, you can secure yourself by placing your feet behind them and perform ab crunches while the bench is in the incline position, allowing you to add more variation to your workout! 
	
2" Storage Peg Adaptor 
Olympic Style Bumper Plates

title: Body-Solid Pro Clubline (LVSP) Leverage Shoulder Press Machine - Adjustable Gas-Assisted Arms, Converging Movement, Independent Unilateral Action, Sealed Bearings, Weight Plate Storage
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Benches › Adjustable Benches
description: The Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Shoulder Press (LVSP) is designed for serious, heavy lifting in professional gyms or at home. A converging press arm and independent, unilateral arm action deliver balanced muscle development for the upper body. Ergonomically designed multi-grips offer different positional options, with gas-assisted start positions to get your lift started right. The press arms and seat pads are adjustable to fit users of all sizes.With a 2- by 3-inch 11-gauge high-tensile-strength steel mainframe and double-stitched upholstery, this shoulder workout bench is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. Sealed bearing pivot points provide smooth, friction-free movement through every intense workout. Weight plate holders are built into the shoulder press bench for easy storage (plates sold separately).When assembled, the Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Shoulder Press measures 49 by 53 by 52 inches inches (L x W x H) and weighs 171 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home Warranty and Full Commercial Warranty.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

OPTIMIZED FOR PERFORMANCE: Designed with converging press arm movement, mimicking natural biomechanics for optimal muscle engagement. With features like sealed bearing pivot points and weight plate holders for storage, it offers a seamless workout experience, allowing you to focus on hitting those chest and shoulder gains efficiently.

BALANCED MUSCLE DEVELOPMENT: This machine supports intense chest and shoulder workouts with its leverage gym design, allowing for a wide range of plate loaded exercises. The independent arm movement ensures balanced development across all muscle groups, while the weight plate holders add convenience by keeping your space organized and your weights within reach.

GASS ASSISTED ADJUSTABLE SEAT: Our leverage shoulder press boasts a gas-assisted adjustable seat pad, ensuring comfort for all user sizes. With adjustable press arms and independent, unilateral arm movement, it offers a customizable workout that targets specific muscles and provides the versatility needed for a comprehensive shoulder and chest training routine.

DIMENSIONS: Engineered with a robust 2" x 3" 11-gauge steel mainframe and electrostatically applied metallic silver powder coat paint finish, ensuring durability and resistance to wear and tear. Measures 49"x53"x52" and weighs 207lbs.

Transform Your Home Gym, Transform Your Body 
The Smith machine is a piece of equipment commonly used in home gyms for a full body workout. It can be especially helpful for women or beginners who are new to the gym. The equipment has a barbell supported on each side and a pulley system that moves the weights. The bar moves up and down on a track, and safety bars restrict the bar from moving further than desired. The springs in the smith machine also absorb some impact, preventing injuries. 
There are several reasons why one might use a Smith machine, including: 
To become familiar with a specific exercise and its proper form before attempting it with free weights.
To isolate a particular group of muscles for strength training or to address muscle imbalances.
To prepare for an exercise that you are not yet able to do with free weights.
To alleviate nervousness about trying free weight movements, such as squats, deadlifts, or hip thrusts, for the first time.
To practice the movement pattern and foot placement and get comfortable with the bar without having to manage a standard 45-pound barbell on your shoulders or in your hands.
The Smith machine can be used in conjunction with other fitness equipment and accessories, such as a workout bench, squat rack, cable attachments, and a pull-up bar, to provide more exercise options. One can use a functional trainer with the Smith machine to do basic exercises such as cable fly, lat pulldown, horizontal bar and parallel bars, low bar pull-up, barbell deadlift, barbell squat, push-up, and pull-up. The workout bench provides more workout options, including seated leg extension, lying leg extension, upper body stretches, and incline, decline, and flat barbell chest press. The Smith machine can also be used as part of an all-in-one cage or Altas Strength home gym equipment, which includes a leg press, arm curl, and other attachments. 
Overall, the Smith machine is an excellent choice for those looking to exercise at home, as it provides a safe and effective way to target various muscle groups while minimizing the risk of injury.

items.text: The vertical leg press attachment quickly transforms into a low row station footpad that combines with either cable pulley system to deliver a full-body workout.

items.name: Rotating Landmine
items.text: Includes a rotating landmine station that is suited for all types of rotational torso training and allows for a wide range of upper body training when connected to an optional barbell (not included).

modules.title: The 8-In-1 Home Gym Solution – Altas Strength 3059 Smith Machine!

aiReviewsSummary.text: Customers find the strength training machine has smooth operation and good build quality. They mention the cables run smoothly and it's easy to transition between workouts. However, some customers find assembly a bit difficult with poor instructions.
